Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配备着以电脑为导航系统的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“CYBER F0RMULA”正式登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替“F-l”的2l世纪赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令全世界人都狂热起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,!Effect,新世纪GPX “CYBER F0RMULA”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思议的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来自你求助的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从昨夜开始一直感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突如其来的风暴阻挡了前进的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿望便浮现在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是喜欢 是奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都会放在心上 不论什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的波浪会紧随而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上出发 决不动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了实现梦想 永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管生阿斯拉达车队已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四战的场地加拿大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行车子的检修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.72,0:02:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拿大  这里有太多的回忆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.29,0:02:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十话 耳环的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 新引擎的效果怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才试的结果连续弯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.70,0:02:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像还不行耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转弯后的加速力量不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.73,0:03:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一周后就要比赛了 你记得在比赛前调整好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再试一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就再试一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事啊 明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想出去一下好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾经跟我说过 你来过加拿大一次对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以有一个地方 我想再去一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.36,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你去吧 这里你就别担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 车田叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在黄昏以前我会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖的待在家里喔 武八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达 你已经没力气了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样在弯道过后的加速力会不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降低引擎转速 危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把二档的齿轮比提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.96,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们继续冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达 引擎缩缸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才我们在绕最后一个弯道的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎突然出了毛病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.88,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会叫牵引车去修的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈特·修马赫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快闪开 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.44,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你停下来干什么 快走 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈特·修马赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候…你为什么要救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许愿瀑布跟七年前一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明日香 这个瀑布叫许愿瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许愿瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在瀑布前面许愿的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的愿望就会实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要许的愿望就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望我们全家在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还能够到这个地方来玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.13,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我们最后一次的全家旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥 你为何不跟我们联络呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以为你一定会来看比赛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈特·修马赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是很重要的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个跟你又没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 也对 再见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才我口气不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次比赛还承你救了隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是我哥哥的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们五年前分手之后 就再没见过面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们聊聊好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么要来这个地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这里有我的回忆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前跟父母哥哥一起来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道这个瀑布的名字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 叫许愿瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 你经常一个人到这个地方来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么这么问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.09,0:08:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…因为这个地方并不是很有名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么会知道这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.03,0:08:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我偶尔来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶尔来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达的情况怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是来探听消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说阿斯拉达换新引擎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于赛车的事情我不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我可是老板的代理人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老板代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许愿瀑布也许并非全是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说阿修就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是以前我们队里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.36,0:09:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,F1赛车手阿修啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.04,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来修马赫就是阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是管生修啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.08,0:09:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三年前我是队里第一个赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我没有想到他也出现在那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.53,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成绩很好 不愧是艾迪利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.97,0:09:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 他是从今天起成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们专业驾驶员的阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请各位多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是驾驶员队长艾迪利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常高兴能够见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不知道的你就问我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修在去年的F3成绩非常的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一次的队内第一驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要从大家里面选出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然阿修也包括在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那个时候开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修就成了我的竞争对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第一次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶选拔赛的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和阿修互相竞争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太操之过急发生了车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤了左眼和一只手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是本公司的机械人研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是宇宙开发的一环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想不想要试一试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赛车是我的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能够再让我握方向盘\N再怎么试都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是我就装了公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.79,0:11:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最新发明的义肢还有义眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在经过地狱般的训练之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成了最强的赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要从别队转来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底想要干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再问你一个问题好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.87,0:12:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人是自己要参加高智能方程式赛车的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是关于隼人的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 为什么要问呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高智能方程式它虽然重视安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只要稍微有差错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会有生命危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小孩子开太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你又为什么要来参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种有危险的赛车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了测试自己的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人都是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们老是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.82,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去英国 爸爸 可不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想让你驾驶阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么高智能方程式你不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以电脑系统的好坏来决定胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.67,0:13:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那根本就没有什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要凭我自己的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到世界第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确 电脑系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以超越人类极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过呢再好的电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是要人才能操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人跟电脑互相配合起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样才能获得最后胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一点跟普通的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.69,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有什么两样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.86,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸 你只不过要我帮你完成\N你当年没有完成的梦想罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.37,0:13:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给我住嘴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 你为什么要打哥哥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明日香 保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想去吗 跟我去兜风?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然被邀请 我觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是生长在绅士之国的英国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会好好的把你送回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.50,0:15:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办啊  我不能随便上车的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.11,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去晚了的话  又要被车田叔骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想带你到一个地方去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到现在我才发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有点像哥哥耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家店我非常喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我来加拿大一定会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过带女孩子来这倒是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么啦  你不想知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才不是已经说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天黑之前我一定会送你回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我可以问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么要对我这么好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一个年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你差不多的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.91,0:18:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  你又为什么不拒绝我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就跟你一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过我有一个年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你差不多的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 别说了 汤趁热喝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.87,0:18:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像这样我觉得好温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.88,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然想起我哥哥来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修马赫先生 你为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是要戴着墨镜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一次赛车的时候我受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想让别人看见那个伤疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哥哥也是一个赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他参加过英国的方程式赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我们一直没有联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是英国的赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么你知不知道我哥哥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.71,0:19:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫做阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸虽然责备过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他现在也很担心他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太阳就快要下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你哥哥他一定也很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要他还有梦想在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人只要有梦想 再怎么苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也一定会活得下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你请我这么丰盛的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈特·修马赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一个年纪跟你差不多的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么你又为什么没有拒绝我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.12,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过我有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你年纪差不多的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你哥哥他一定会很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是修哥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.79,0:20:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对哥哥来说 许愿瀑布\N也是一个值得回忆的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不会去那里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么会来这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道这个瀑布叫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 他一定是哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是久违了 营生修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错吧 奈特·修马赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.54,0:21:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么又回到我的面前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经什么都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.11,0:21:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为了要升官\N你做了所有卑鄙的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及你想做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告诉你我绝对不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.95,0:21:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你继续为恶下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底知道了多少 营生修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他人目光没有在背后注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为肩负着使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下双手 仰望天空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有现在加倍努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能有明天的辉煌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 不用后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向着自己树立的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎着风前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终我们会是胜利者

